    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事情节/出场人物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[阿西, 美女室友竟然...？]是一款 FMV 真人视频恋爱游戏，你将以第一人称与5位美女室友一起体验别样合租生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本作中，您将扮演合租公寓的房东男主 吴宥万(直译:牛奶男)，一直独来独往的你，生活中突然闯入 <strong>5 位性格各异美女租客</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们之间又将擦出怎样的火花呢？最后陪在你身边的会是谁呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第一位租客，相识20年的青梅竹马：高末淑</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/a65d55968ac5d1e218b7d6bdf0ecaff7.poster.avif?t=1772170494\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/a65d55968ac5d1e218b7d6bdf0ecaff7.webm?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/a65d55968ac5d1e218b7d6bdf0ecaff7.mp4?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;你真的..只把我当朋友吗？&quot;</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第二位租客，初恋白月光, 过气偶像：朴敏静</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/9ccadc383b7022e41c6af1f43d45dbf9.poster.avif?t=1772170494\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/9ccadc383b7022e41c6af1f43d45dbf9.webm?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/9ccadc383b7022e41c6af1f43d45dbf9.mp4?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;我和哥哥的关系，不想只限于歌手和粉丝...&quot;</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第三位租客，难搞的职场上司姐姐：佟圆圆</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/18bbbf73684de65ee523adce1c19ece5.poster.avif?t=1772170494\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/18bbbf73684de65ee523adce1c19ece5.webm?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/18bbbf73684de65ee523adce1c19ece5.mp4?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;诶~ 真可爱，原来你喜欢这种play...？&quot;</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第四位租客，天然呆的直球妹妹：高恩妃</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/a0507048212946e312ee9510e6bdb659.poster.avif?t=1772170494\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/a0507048212946e312ee9510e6bdb659.webm?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/a0507048212946e312ee9510e6bdb659.mp4?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;哥哥! 请和我结婚吧！&quot;</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第五位租客，可爱的孤僻社恐宅女：曹圣依</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/432797e3a7a0a2a5b3f701b9e2007ced.poster.avif?t=1772170494\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/432797e3a7a0a2a5b3f701b9e2007ced.webm?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/432797e3a7a0a2a5b3f701b9e2007ced.mp4?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;你...你是来救我的吗..?! &quot;</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各类美女的轮番攻势下，是一心一意，爱我所爱；还是来者不拒，雨露均沾？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亦或是一不小心迎来BAD END，又或者……你还能找到另一种别样的爱情（？） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>亮点介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第一人称沉浸式恋爱模拟游戏</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/2d234a7c20822c10d4bc4f307d3a9d49.poster.avif?t=1772170494\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/2d234a7c20822c10d4bc4f307d3a9d49.webm?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/2d234a7c20822c10d4bc4f307d3a9d49.mp4?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >: 本游戏从头至尾以第一视角进行游戏。你将在各种引人入胜的事件中做出决定和选择。在游戏中，你将置身于真实发生在生活中的情节与场景，无论是温馨的合租日常、怦然心动的约会时刻，还是让人脸红心跳的暧昧互动，都将由你亲自体验、选择与改变！这不仅仅是一款恋爱模拟游戏，更是一款关于选择和爱情的游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的故事情节</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/bac071cc7d568744760cdda512647971.avif?t=1772170494\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >: 在这款游戏中，你的每一个选择都将影响故事的走向，带来完全不同的体验！我们为您精心设计了百余种故事分支、十几种截然不同的结局，让您能够反复探索、深入挖掘这场恋爱旅程的每一个可能性。每章中隐藏的后记和奖励视频将丰富您的模拟体验。意想不到的选择可能会解锁隐藏彩蛋视频哦~~或许是一场未曾曝光的甜蜜约会，或许是某位女主角不为人知的内心独白，或许是....... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自然的演技和高质量的视觉效果</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/52dbe9c88b6273e933003e3b551ed027.poster.avif?t=1772170494\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/52dbe9c88b6273e933003e3b551ed027.webm?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/52dbe9c88b6273e933003e3b551ed027.mp4?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >: 这款游戏全程由人气油管博主真人出演，以自然流畅的演技与高水准的视觉呈现，让你仿佛置身于一场真实的恋爱故事之中。与五位可爱的女主角一起，体验身临其境的恋爱心动的感觉！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们与专业电影导演合作，采用超高质量的影像呈现，精美的画面细腻还原每一个动作与表情，让玩家仿佛亲临现场，与心仪的女孩面对面交流。打造出一场既具电影质感，又充满互动性的恋爱体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>魅力无法抵挡的女主角们</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/b9cc40f00aa792b8c65f37acbfa58480.poster.avif?t=1772170494\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/b9cc40f00aa792b8c65f37acbfa58480.webm?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/b9cc40f00aa792b8c65f37acbfa58480.mp4?t=1772170494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >: “口嫌体正直”的青梅竹马，到慢慢依赖你信任你的过气小偶像，从霸道又透露着可爱的职场上司姐姐，到直率可爱，满眼是你的直球妹妹，甚至还有阁楼上的神秘房客等你解锁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一位都有独特的魅力，保证总有一位能让你心动！相信总有一位会是你的菜！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于我们</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好，我们是Storytaco制作组。正如我们公司名字，我们希望能像塔可（墨西哥卷饼）一样，为大家带来内容丰富、充满美味与乐趣的精彩剧情体验。我们一直致力于为玩家呈现引人入胜的故事和沉浸式的剧情体验，我们深知每位玩家都是独立的个体，都有独特的情感需求，游戏不仅是单纯的娱乐消遣，作为第九艺术，游戏更是让每个人在其中体验人生百态的机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一家韩国公司，我们不仅专注于创作高质量的游戏内容，更非常重视中国玩家的需求与反馈，力求打造符合中国市场的优质体验。我们的团队始终相信，好的游戏体验是跨越文化与国界的，玩家和制作组也是双向奔赴的。因为中国玩家的支持与喜爱，我们才有了动力去追求更好的创作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从中国大热的《完蛋，被美女包围了》开始，我们接触到了互动影游这一全新的游戏形式。它是影像和游戏的完美结合，让玩家不仅能身临其境地参与剧情，还能在其中体验更深刻、更真实的情感互动。我们希望能借影游的形式打破语言的壁垒，把这种新的情感体验带给全球的玩家，尤其是我们重视的中国玩家。因为我们想让你知道，每位玩家的感受对我们来说非常重要。我们会一直努力，带给你更多触动心灵的游戏体验，期待和你一起在这个充满情感与故事的世界里，一起走得更远。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021100/extras/84f586828c1785648c779ee4a9375a4a.avif?t=1772170494\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
